::Blue Reeker::

Blue Reeker hear gun shots and the retreat of some bo that she doesn't know. 
She lays there in her pod. She reaches up and types into the computer to 
start scanning for a life form.

The wolves surrond the skunks not really caring about the battle that is 
going on.

Slowly the pod door open and out steps Blue Reeker. She is in her giant 
Skunk form. She jumps over Zardus and attacks the wolves slashing at them 
with her claws

The wolves turn around in run in retreat.
